ygData.messageBody:
It is very easy to delete the ones that are about twinking. Obviously with
everyone replying there is an interest and varying opinions on the subject.
I guess I could make a EQ_Twinking mailing list :) I don't mind reading off
topic discussions as long as they are interesting. At least we are
discussing the twinking of bards :)
